Ashes of Time Redux;;76;;78;;R;;When his friend Huang (Tony Leung Ka Fai) visits mercenary Ou-yang (Leslie Cheung), they trade stories including that of princess Mu-rong (Brigitte Lin), who is alternately male and female. Peach Blossom (Carina Lau) quarrels with her blind husband (Tony Leung Chiu Wai), a swordsman who wants to avenge the bereavement of a peasant girl (Maggie Cheung). The girl also attracts the favors of the swordsman Hung Chi (Jacky Cheung), who is forever trailed by his doting wife (Li Bai).;;Action;;Kar-Wai Wong;;2008;;Jacky Cheung,Leslie Cheung,Maggie Cheung,Carina Lau,Tony Leung Chiu Wai,Tony Ka Fai Leung,Brigitte Lin,Li Bai;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ashes_of_time_redux_2008